name: dayplanner
0:

”Alexa, i'm bored”
”Alexa, give me something to do”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: day planner
des:
You can get Alexa to give you ideas of what to do during the day just by simply saying "Alexa, what should i do".
For example it could reply with "You could try going on a walk. "
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
